Architectural notes
-------------------

The designs specific to c3x — the declarative TOML catalog, the
pipeline-stage HCL evaluator, the four-state verifier
(OK/STATIC/FREE/ZERO), the on-disk SQLite price cache, the
recommendation rules, the --what-if override syntax — originated with
this project.
